{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1682992, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 330585, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "人有个巨强的先验的语言模型，很可能是刻在DNA里的（迫真", "timestamp": 1621355280, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1682994, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 330585, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "读英语读多了，自然会一些陌生词的发音，猜词义，这不就是基于统计吗", "timestamp": 1621355282, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1682997, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 330585, "reply_to": 1682992, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice:兄弟细说", "timestamp": 1621355300, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1683000, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 330585, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有先验了之后学啥都特别快", "timestamp": 1621355309, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1683006, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 330585, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我不知道在哪看到过一篇文章，说人学母语和学外语的机制是不一样的。这篇研究意味着人的母语是有不同于外语的先验在的", "timestamp": 1621355358, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1683009, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 330585, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "同理，小孩认东西都是小样本（相对于CNN而言），说明图像也在人脑里有先验", "timestamp": 1621355406, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1683014, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 330585, "reply_to": 1683009, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 有道理，所以咱们要把这个先验的库先造出来", "timestamp": 1621355437, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1683025, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 330585, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "原D的问题是个强AI经典问题，AI是不一定非得照着人脑，那你就只能用一堆数据去填鸭呗…", "timestamp": 1621355490, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1683027, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 330585, "reply_to": 1683006, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 母语只不过是第一个学的而已，和基因没太大关系。", "timestamp": 1621355511, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1683035, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 330585, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在我看来就两条路，要么把人脑整明白然后仿真，要么借鉴人脑怼数据量，力大砖飞", "timestamp": 1621355540, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1683050, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 330585, "reply_to": 1683027, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 随便找的一篇新闻 https://www.i21st.cn/article/tesol/23834_1.html\n目前学界主流观点就是母语学习有个先验，而且是很强的先验", "timestamp": 1621355652, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1683104, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 330585, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "草，A君怕不是乔姆斯基的信徒", "timestamp": 1621356059, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1683259, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 330585, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "毕竟现在搞nlp的都是以编程为主，搞语言学的都没几个", "timestamp": 1621358053, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1683267, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 330585, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "语言学是认为人学习母语是有一套模板的，参chomsky", "timestamp": 1621358100, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1683590, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 330585, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "现在大样本搞出来的预训练模型，再做fine-tune可以理解为有先验吧？刚接触了解不深，可以讨论下", "timestamp": 1621369232, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 330585, "reply": 15, "tag": null, "text": "#330538\n难道咱们对语言的习得，或者说所谓的语感，不就是基于统计的吗？\n我是这样理解的", "timestamp": 1621355220, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1621369231, "url": "", "vote": {}}}